description:
Darkness Radio is Cursed by The Conjuring House with guests Cody and Jennifer Heinzen!


What happens when Hollywood meets REAL Horror? Today we visit with the new owners of the house made famous in the fright fest movie, The Conjuring.

We have spoken to past residents, but is the house STILL active? Cody & Jennifer Heinzen drop by to fill us in on the history and haunting of this famous house, PLUS we discuss the upcoming Live Paranormal Experiment that will be taking place there for the whole world to witness, May 9-16th!
